3b51a7c6-a0a9-4e5a-a7ae-af452777d7d2.title: Left to Survive
3b51a7c6-a0a9-4e5a-a7ae-af452777d7d2.summary: Left To Survive is a game about life after apocalypse – zombies have enslaved the Earth and survival war has begun! Life is no longer what it used to be: humans are fighting for survival, and the Earth belongs to the undead from now on.

318e823e-8247-466b-8fd3-de5ed8e1da51.title: Lady Popular
318e823e-8247-466b-8fd3-de5ed8e1da51.summary: Lady Popular is a casual dress-up game that aims primarily at a female audience. Lady Popular has been translated into 21 languages and has over 8 million registered users.

40938132-7757-44a0-9cd6-efb720faf9a9.title: Mincraft
40938132-7757-44a0-9cd6-efb720faf9a9.summary: Minecraft is a game made up of blocks, creatures, and community. You can survive the night or build a work of art – the choice is all yours. But if the thought of exploring a vast new world all on your own feels overwhelming, then fear not!
